Pawn

236
00:19:47.330 --> 00:19:48.200
Pawn

237
00:19:47.330 --> 00:19:47.370
Shop

238
00:19:47.370 --> 00:19:47.410
Shop

239
00:19:47.410 --> 00:19:47.450
Shop

240
00:19:47.450 --> 00:19:47.490
Shop

241
00:19:47.490 --> 00:19:47.540
Shop

242
00:19:47.540 --> 00:19:47.580
Shop

243
00:19:47.580 --> 00:19:48.200
Shop

244
00:19:48.200 --> 00:19:48.200
Pawn Shop

245
00:19:48.200 --> 00:19:52.790
Pawn
Shop

246
00:19:49.210 --> 00:19:52.790
Blueprints pawned ten years ago?

247
00:19:53.510 --> 00:19:56.670
It's rare that we would ever take those...

248
00:19:58.990 --> 00:20:00.380
Oh, maybe those!

249
00:20:00.380 --> 00:20:02.720
What? Do you have them?!

250
00:20:02.720 --> 00:20:07.070
Well, of course, they've long since
gone to somebody else...

251
00:20:07.070 --> 00:20:09.770
